(78, 1, '2021-08-01 04:44:53', '2021-08-01 04:44:53', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch c th t hng trc tuyn  website Cu t thng qua cc bc t hng c bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vui lng tham kho thng tin chi tit v tng bc t hng nh sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>1. ng nhp ti khon ti Cu t:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch vui lng ng nhp bng ti khon  c  Cu t hoc ng nhp thng qua Facebook/ Zalo/ Google. Trong trng hp cha ng k ti khon , qu khch c th chn dng To ti khon  ng k ti khon ti Cu t.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi  hon tt, qu khch c th bm vo ch To ti khon  hon tt qu trnh ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>2. Tm kim sn phm:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch c th tm sn phm theo 3 cch:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>G tn sn phm vo thanh tm kim.<br>Tm theo danh mc.<br>Tm theo cc sn phm mi nht, bn chy hoc danh mc ph bin trn tng ngnh hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>3. Thm sn phm vo gi hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi  tm c sn phm mong mun, qu khch vui lng bm vo hnh hoc tn sn phm  vo c trang thng tin chi tit ca sn phm, sau :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kim tra thng tin sn phm: gi, thng tin khuyn mi.<br>Chn s lng mong mun.<br>Thm sn phm vo gi hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi  thao tc b sn phm u tin vo n hng, qu khch vui lng thc hin cc bc sau  thm cc sn phm khc vo gi hng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chn vo logo Cu t  tr v trang ch hoc g tm kim sn phm trn thanh cng c.<br>Thm sn phm vo gi hng bng cch chn s lng v Chn mua.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Qu trnh ny c th lp li cho n khi qu khch hon tt vic b tt c cc sn phm cn t mua vo gi hng</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>4. Kim tra gi hng v t hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch c th t cc sn phm khc nhau trong 1 gi hng thnh 1 n hng, cc sn phm trong gi hng s c ng thnh 1 kin hng (nu sn phm thuc cng 1 nh cung cp/kho x l) v giao n a ch qu khch  ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi qu khch  c  sn phm cn t trong gi hng, vui lng m gim gi (nu c) v tip tc cc bc sau  t hng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chn sn phm qu khch mun mua v iu chnh s lng ph hp.<br>Bm Mua hng  bt u t hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>5. iu chnh a ch giao hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>6. Chn phng thc thanh ton, s dng Cu t Xu v t Mua:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cu t h tr giao hng v thanh ton tn ni cho cc n hng c tng tr gi t 20.000.000 tr xung trn ton quc. Qu khch vui lng tham kho thm ti: Cc Phng Thc Thanh Ton</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi hon tt qu trnh chn phng thc thanh ton, vui lng kim tra li cc thng tin sau: xut ha n VAT (nu c), a ch nhn hng, gi khuyn mi, tng tin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu cc thng tin trn  chnh xc, qu khch vui lng bm t Mua, h thng s bt u tin hnh to n hng da trn cc thng tin qu khch  ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>7. Kim tra v xc nhn n hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi hon tt c bc t mua, h thng s gi n qu khch mt m s n hng v thng bo thi gian giao hng d kin, qu khch c th kim tra li n hng bng cch bm vo dng n hng ca ti hoc email xc nhn n hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>8. Theo di tnh trng n hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi t hng thnh cng, qu khch c th theo di tin trnh x l v vn chuyn ca n hng bng cch ng nhp vo ng link:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>L<strong>u :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cu t khuyn khch qu khch t thao tc t hng  c th tham gia u i v theo di tnh trng n hng. Trng hp qu khch yu cu Cu t h tr t hng thay Cu t rt tic cha p dng Cu t Xu, bookcare, coupon cho n hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Hng dn mua hng', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'huong-dan-mua-hang', '', '', '2021-08-21 19:56:00', '2021-08-21 12:56:00', '', 0, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?page_id=78', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(79, 1, '2021-08-01 04:45:07', '2021-08-01 04:45:07', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Khu vc p dng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>p dng cho tt c a ch giao hng trong lnh th Vit Nam.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Thi gian giao hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thi gian vn chuyn ph thuc vo kho x l v a ch nhn hng. Qu khch vui lng tham kho thi gian giao hng d kin ti trang sn phm bng cch vo thng tin sn phm, in thng tin vo khu vc giao hng: tnh/thnh, qun/huyn, phng/x.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi hon tt, h thng s thng bo n qu khch thi gian giao hng d kin cho sn phm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngoi ra, qu khch c th kim tra thi gian nhn hng v cc ph vn chuyn ti bc 3 \"Thanh ton&amp; t mua\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*<strong>Lu </strong>: thi gian giao hng trn ch th hin d kin, thc t c th dao ng sm hoc mun hn ty theo sn phm qu khch t mua. Qu khch c th s dng tnh nng \"Tra cu n hng\"  theo di qu trnh x l n hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Ngy hiu lc chnh sch 19/03/2010.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Chnh sch giao hng', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chinh-sach-giao-hang', '', '', '2021-08-21 19:37:12', '2021-08-21 12:37:12', '', 0, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?page_id=79', 0, 'page', '', 0),
