(133, 1, '2021-08-02 18:15:02', '2021-08-02 18:15:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> c c mt ly c ph ng v th ngoi yu t chnh l c ph th phn quan trng c ch  chnh l  si nng ca nc pha c ph. Bnh thng chng ta lun dng nc si 100*C v  an ton ca nc nhng dng nh vy vi c ph liu c ng. u l nhit  nc ph hp nht  c tch c ph thm m v. Cn lu  g  tch caf t chun sc  hng  v?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-left\"><strong> quan trng ca nhit  nc i vi cafe</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ht cafe cha nhiu acid, du t nhin v cc hp cht khc. Khi chit xut c ph, nc ng vi tr tch cc hp cht  ra khi ht cafe v ha tan vi chng. Yu t quyt nh  ha tan cng nh hng n hng v ca cafe l nhit  ca nc pha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu nhit  nc thp s lm cafe c v mng,  snh thp. Nhng nu nhit  tng ln th cc hp cht trong ht cafe c chit xut tt v nhanh hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi nhit  nc thch hp bn s cm nhn c v cafe r rng, tinh t v phong ph hn. Vi nhit  cao s din ra qu trnh bay hi gii phng kh cc hp cht trong cafe vo khng kh. V th d  khong cch xa bn vn cm nhn c hng thm c trng ca cafe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>u l nhit  tt nht cho cafe ?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thi gian chit xut ph thuc nhiu vo nhit  nc pha vy th u l nhit  ph hp cho mt tch cafe. Chng ta cng c mt quan nim sai lm rng nc cng nng th cafe cng ngon, nhng s tht khng phi nh vy. T mt nghin cu ch ra nhit  nc l tng nht  chit xut caf cn bng hng thm,  chua, v ng v v ngt l t 90  96  C (khong 194  205F).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":548,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/nhiet-do-ly-tuong-cho-mot-ly-cf-clc-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-548\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lc bn dng nc  nhit  thp hn mt s hp cht quan trng trong caf s khng c chit xut v bn s khng thu c tch caf c hng v nh .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vy nhit  nc qu cao th sao, lc y mt s hp cht nh du, cht lm ng ha tan mnh. iu ny s lm ly caf ca bn b ng gt hoc c v chy. Song song khi dng nhit  cao sn sinh ra nhiu cht trong cafe khng tt cho sc khe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Kim sot hng v bng nhit  nc pha</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu bn mun thng thc mt ly cafe chun v hy pha vi nhit  nc  94-9  C mang cho bn  thm nng, ng v chua cao hp khu v vi mi ngi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>H nhit  thp hn khi bn thch v mng nh, t chua v ng. Nn ch , nu pha  nhit  thp th thi gian chit xut s lu hn. Kiu v ny cng c rt nhiu thc khch u chung nht l phi n.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngoi phng php pha c ph bng nc nng truyn thng chng ta cn c th ch bin bng nc lnh hoc nc . Nghe tht k l nhng ng l chng c tht, do nhit  thp nn cng on s lu hn, bn phi  cafe t 3 n 18 ting  chit xut nc ct.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tuy nhin ti Vit Nam vn theo phng php truyn thng vi nc nng. V n c mt hng v c trng qua nhiu th h nhng vn m du n. C c phng php pha nc hiu qu cn chn ch g na m khng la mt gi cafe cht lng ti Cu t v thc hnh ngay no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'NHIT  L TNG CHO MT LY C PH CHT LNG', ' c c mt ly c ph ng v th ngoi yu t chnh l c ph th phn quan trng c ch  chnh l  si nng ca nc pha c ph. ', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'khong-nen-dung-nuoc-soi-100-do-pha-ca-phe-3', '', '', '2021-08-20 21:29:49', '2021-08-20 14:29:49', '', 0, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=133', 0, 'post', '', 0),
