(512, 2, '2021-08-19 22:35:03', '2021-08-19 15:35:03', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vit Nam l nc c nn vn ha dng c ph lu i, c mi sng khi bn i dc trn ph s thy t cc qun sang trng n nhng hng gnh va h nhng ni no c gc c ph u c cnh n ng u i. K c nhng ai khng c thi gian, h vn n mua mt ly mang i  bt u ngy mi ca h.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vic ung c ph khng cn ph bin cho nhng ngi trng thnh m ngy nay gii tr cng rt u chung. Nhng liu my ai bit c nhng li ch v tc hi pha sau n, cch chng ta dng n mi ngy liu c tt hay khng. Ti y Cu t s cho bn nhng thng tin hu ch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Li ch ca vic ung c ph</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>1. Gim cn hiu qu vi c ph</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>y chc hn l iu c ng o ch em ph n yu thch, trong c ph lun cha mt lng cafein rt cao, thng t 0.9  1.3%. Mt hp cht quan trng thc y lipolysis, gip chuyn ha cc axit bo trong mu v t bo thnh nng lng. T , c ph v tnh khin lng m gim i m t nh hng n lng c nc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":509,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/caphe-giam-giamcan.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-509\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qua nghin cu cho thy caffeine lm tng qu trnh t chy cht bo  ngi gy khong 29% v ngi bo ph 10%. Tuy nhin chng c th b gim tc dng khi bn s dng chng thng xuyn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng tht s bt u mt ngy mi bi mt tch c ph cng khng t ng khng no?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>2. Cung cp nng lng v duy tr tnh to</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng phi t nhin m chng ta a chung dng c ph vo bui sng, c ph c bit n l mt thc ung nh thc con ngi ta, gip ta c mt ngy lm vic y tnh to. Ti sao vy?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thnh phn ca c ph cha cht kch thch tng t vi Adenosine c sn sinh trong no khi chng ta khng ng hoc lm vic. Chng lm cho cc cht dn truyn thn kinh khc nh dopamine v norepinephrine tng ln, t  kch hot mnh m n cc t bo thn kinh. Khi ung c ph, chc nng hot ng ca no s c ci thin nh tm trng, tr nh, tc  phn ng cng nh nng lng trong c th ni chung.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>3. Tng cng sc  khng</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C nhiu li ch m c ph mang li nhng y l li ch m mnh thch nht, mt loi  ung c th gip c th ta khe mnh v bo v bn thn trit . Sc  khng l mt iu quan trng trong c th ta v chng gip ta trnh khi bnh tt v bn bit y d bnh nng hay nh cng mang n nhiu bt li trong cuc sng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu trnh phn hy cht bo  cn to nn cc axit bo t do  y cng c xem l ngun nhin liu cho c th hot ng, thm ch 12% th cht c ci thin. Bn nn th mt tch c ph trc khi tp 30 pht v cm nhn tc dng ca chng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>4. Thc ung chng lo ha hu ch</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hm lng cht chng oxy ha trong cafe cao hn hn cht chng oxy ha c tng hp t tri cy v cc loi rau. T  n c lit k l mt trong cc loi  ung lnh mnh khi cha cht chng oxy ha di do trn th gii. Nh mt thn dc duy tr sc p chng gip bn tr hn v khe hn khi duy tr t 1-2 tch mi ngy ty th trng mi ngi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>5. Phng chng cc loi bnh v nng cao cht lng sng</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vic phng chng cc loi bnh t mt thc ung mang n cng khng cn l lm v c ph cng khng ngoi l. Cng im qua ca ph s gip chng ta phng chng bnh g no?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Gim stress hiu qu</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi cuc sng mang n nhiu lo lng v p lc khin c th bn mt mi, hy dng ngay mt tc c ph gii ta tm tr i no. ng bao gi l l tinh thn ca bn thn, i khi chng ta mang bnh trm cm m khng hay bit v hn ht n ngy cng ph bin hn hin nay nht l vi i tng tr. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":508,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/caphe-giam-stress.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-508\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cafe cha dopamine v serotonin c tc dng gip bn gii ta cng thng nng lng  gip bn th thi lm vic vui v v hiu qu hn.Nghin cu ca Harvard mt ph n mi ngy ung 4 tch c ph tr ln th nguy c b trm cm thp hn 20% vo nm 2011.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Bnh tiu ng Type II c phng nga</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>i tho ng tup 2 l mt trong nhng bnh ph bin hng u, mt trong nhng bi ton kh ca nn y hc th vi v sc nh hng ca n. C ch ca bnh l s tng lng ng trong mu do khng insulin hoc gim kh nng sn xut insulin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C ph mang li nhiu li ch cho bnh nhn i tho ng. Trong c ph c cha cc hot cht c kh nng khng vim chng li s ri lon ni m. Cc loi hp cht trong c ph c th iu tit insulin hiu qu. Tc dng ca c ph  c cc chuyn gia kim chng v cng nhn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Gim nguy c mc bnh ung th</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ung th l bi ton kh ca nn y hc th gii v c ph c th phng chng 2 loi ung th l ung th gan v ung th i trc trng nm top u nguyn nhn gy t vong trn th gii.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nm 2005 mt nghin cu cho thy ung c phn gim nguy c mc bnh ung th gan n 40%. Tiu th 4 - 5 tch c ph gim nguy c ung th i trc trng hn 15% trong mt nghin cu din ra trn 489.706 ngi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>C li vi tim mch v chng t qu</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C ph c th lm tng huyt p nhng n  mc  nh v s n nh nu bn dng chng thng xuyn. Vi hm lng oxy ha trong cafe c cng dng ngn chn cc bnh v cao huyt p v tim mch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":510,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/caphe-tot-cho-tim-mach.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-510\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>iu ny cng gp phn chng cc cn t qu. H tr mu lu thng u, ngn nga x va ng mch v tai bin mch mu no. Nguy c mc t qu  nhng ngi hay ung cafe thp hn n 20%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Gim chng mt tr v phng nga bnh Alzheimer</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bnh Alzheimer cng l cn bnh cha c phng php trit . Tuy nhin vn c nhng cch phng nga bnh nh thay i ch  n ung, tp th dc Nhng t ngi bit, dng cafe cng rt tt trong phng nga Alzheimer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nghin cu cho thy nguy c mc alzheimer  nhng ngi thng dng cafe thp hn ti 65% so vi ngi bnh thng. Bn khng nn lm dng c ph thay nc ung hng ngy v chng ch l sn phm h tr.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Gim nguy c mc bnh Parkinson</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bnh Parkinson cng l bnh thoi ha thn kinh, sau bnh Alzheimer. Bnh ny gy ra ci cht ca cc t bo thn kinh ti dopamine trong no v vn cha c phng php iu tr dt im.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Caffeine trong c ph gip tng  khng, sn sinh ra hp cht c cng dng lm gim nguy c mc bnh Parkinson. C th gim c 60% nguy c mc bnh Parkinson khi bn ung c ph mi ngy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Nhng tc hi ca c ph</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bt k iu g cng c mt tri ca n, song song vi nhng li ch m c ph mang n l nhng tc hi ca chng v d nhin Cu t cng  tm hiu v lit k nhng tc hi y cho bn. Hy l mt ngi dng thng thi, s dng mi th mt cch khoa hc trnh nhng bin chng xu xy n vi chng ta.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>1. Ni khng vi ph n mang thai:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt iu lun c truyn tai nhau  l tc hi ca cafe n ph n mang thai, nhng hp cht caffeine c trong c ph c cnh bo gy hi cho tr, n khin cm xc ca thai ph b ri lon l trm trng hn. iu  c th nh hng n a b, bn cnh  cht Caffeine c th tng kch thch tun hon mu  m khin thai b d tt.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":511,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/caphe-khong-tot-cho-phu-nu-mang-thai.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-511\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>2. Say cafe liu bn tng tri qua?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngi ta hay ni va  l c ci g nhiu qu cng khng tt, vi cht caffeine li l nguyn nhn gy nn chng say cafe, liu bn c bit iu ? L do c cc bc s a ra l khi np qu nhiu caffeine vo c th vo cng mt lc, nhp tim s b ri lon gy ra cm gic au u , hoa mt chong vng, thm ch l nn ma v c th dn n tnh trng co git. Hy ung nhiu nc vo nu bn b say c ph  gim nh cc triu chng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>3. Ung nhiu c ph c liu c tt?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ung c ph ng l  ci thin tinh thn tnh to khi lm vic v hc tp nhng phi  liu lng va phi. Nu duy tr thi quen ung qu nhiu cafe s gy hi cho sc khe. Hn ht s khin tng nhp tim huyt p cao, tay chn run ry thm ch l mt mi bun nn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>4. nh hng n d dy v h tiu ha:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong c ph c cha caffeine lm tng tn sut cc cn co tht  h tiu ha lm au bao t v axit trong cafe lm tng sn xut axit d dy, gy kh chu nh: y hi, co tht d dy,  chua; khin gy tn thng d dy vi nhng ngi mn cm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Th trng mi ngi u c mt ngng yu cu nht nh cho tng cht dinh dng c np vo c th v th hy v mt li sng khoa hc hy tm hiu tht k nhng mn n, thc ung m bn dng. Hy dng chng khoa hc, lng nghe c th bn cn g  cung cp hp l. Cm n  c bi vit t Cu t v ng ngn ngi s dng sn phm ca chng ti c ph c sn cht lng cao lm hi lng nhng khch hng kh tnh nht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'LI CH V TC HI CA C PH M BN NN BIT', 'C ph l thc ung yu thch ca rt nhiu ngi. Cc tn  cafe cng khng th bt u ngy mi nng ng m khng dng tch c ph. C ph a dng v ph bin l th, vy nhng tc dng ca c ph l g hay ung cafe c tc dng g? C ph c li hay c hi i vi sc khe ca bn th no? ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '295-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-19 22:35:03', '2021-08-19 15:35:03', '', 295, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=512', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
