(522, 2, '2021-08-20 10:42:15', '2021-08-20 03:42:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Duy tr cn nng v c mt vc dng tuyt vi lun l mi quan tm ca nhiu ch em ph n. H chu th nhiu cch khc nhau  c thn hnh mong mun v gim cn bng cch ung cafe cng khng phi ngoi l. Phng php ny khng qu ph bin v cafe khng phi l mn khoi khu ca hu ht ch em nhng liu tht s chng c tc dng n vy, hy cng Cu t xem th no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Ti sao c ph c th gim cn?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cht caffeine c trong c ph c tc dng kch thch h thn kinh trung ng, lm tinh thn tnh to khi b mt mi. c bit, caffeine l cht sinh nhit tt v l cht kch thch trao i cht, gip axit bo trong mu chuyn ha thnh nng lng d tiu th.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ni chung cht trong c ph thc y qu trnh t chy cht bo, nh bay m tha trong c th bn cnh , caffeine cn c tc dng li tiu gip ti cc c t trong c th ra ngoi mt cch an ton.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>iu  nghe tht hp l nhng li c mt s  kin tri chiu rng h cng dng c ph nhng khng mang li hiu qu gim cn nh  ni. Mu cht  y l bn lun phi hiu cch dng nh th no  t c kt qu mong mun c, vy u l phng php chnh xc cho cafe gim cn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Gim cn cng c ph ng cch</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hy dng mt tch c ph en khng ng sau khi n t 30 n 60 pht  l li khuyn t cc chuyn gia, lm vy bn s gim bo bng mt cch nhanh chng t cc cht c trong c ph gip t chy m tha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nn s dng c ph en, khng ng v nng bi v nh th s gip gii ta nng lng trong c th bn nhanh hn. Hn ht nn dng c ph rang xay thay v c ph ha tan v khi  lng caffeine trong c ph khng b gim i do ch bin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ch  gim cn lun hiu qu hn khi kt hp vi vic tp luyn th thao, bn c th dng 1 tch c ph nng hi khong 30 pht trc bui tp, iu ny s gip cho cc axit bo s chuyn ha thnh nng lng, gip tng tc  t chy m hn na.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":509,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/caphe-giam-giamcan.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-509\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bui sng hy np mt tch c ph gip bn c ch cm gic i v bn s khng np nhiu thc n vo c th.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tuy nhin hy lm iu ny mt cch khoa hc nht vi c th ca bn v trnh lm dng n. Bn trong cafe lun c caffeine v nu bn hp th qu mc s dn n vn  tim mch, kim sot c trong c th, hay b gim kali v tnh li tiu ca caffeine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Mt s lu  dnh cho bn khi dng cafe gim cn</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Ni khng vi c ph c</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pha v ung ngay mt tch c ph nng m v s gip bn cm nhn tt hn v cafe. Trnh s dng c ph  qua ngy, chng b tc ng bi yu t mi trng khng cn mang li hng v ngon v c cc cht dinh dng c trong c ph cng b bin i c th nh hng n h tiu ha ca bn nh ri lon tiu ha, bun nn, tiu chy,  v tim tng nhng bnh nguy him cho c th bn. Cho nn hy lun dng nhng tch c ph ti mi trong ngy thi nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Ni khng vi cafe nhi</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C rt nhiu loi c ph c by bn trn th trng v bn ch nn tinh dng nhng thng hiu ni ting v lu i.  cng l tiu ch ca Cu t khi cung cp sn phm cho ngi dng, m bo khng lm cafe gi (nhi) cafe nguyn cht, hoc ln cc tp cht khc. Cht lng ca nhng loi cafe ny khng m bo, c nguy c gy hi cho ngi ung. Cu t hng n sc khe cng ng v cht lng sn phm t c ph c sn cht lng cao.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Ung c ph iu </strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi 2/3ly mt ngy l lng cafe m ngi bo phi np vo c th v duy tr chng trong nhiu thng  c th gim cn thnh cng. L trnh gim cn s thnh cng khi bn tun th nghim tc cc quy tc trong qu trnh gim cn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nguyn tc gim cn nh sau: bn dng mt tch cafe sau khi n 30-60 pht sau  hot ng nh  cc cht trong cafe lm vic hiu qu hn. Lu  hy ung trong mt khung gi nht nh  c hiu qu cao hn nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":521,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/caudat-giam-can-hieu-qua-vs-cafe-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-521\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>B sung thm nhiu nc</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nc vn l thnh phn ng vai tr quan trng n gip bn ha tan cafe nhanh hn. Cafe khin ta c cm gic khng thng xuyn kht nc nu bn khng chu ung nc, th c hng ca bn s lu li v ng cafe. N c th lm bn b i hoc bun nn bt c lc no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hy lun l ngi dng thng thi khi s dng sn phm v cafe Cu t s khng lm bn tht vng. n vi chng ti  cm nhn r hn hng v cafe nguyn cht m .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'GIM CN BNG CAFE THT S C HIU QU?', 'Duy tr cn nng v c mt vc dng tuyt vi lun l mi quan tm ca nhiu ch em ph n. H chu th nhiu cch khc nhau  c thn hnh mong mun v gim cn bng cch ung cafe cng khng phi ngoi l. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '283-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-20 10:42:15', '2021-08-20 03:42:15', '', 283, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=522', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
