(533, 2, '2021-08-20 14:20:31', '2021-08-20 07:20:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt ly c ph nng hi c dng vi mt mn n km  l mt cch thng thc quen thuc, nht l cc bn tr tui thi nay. Nhng qun cafe ph tr nn thn thuc hn vi mi tng lp, h n  th gin, hc tp, hay l tm mt khng gian lm vic, ... u c im chung rng rt yu thich  ngt v nhng mn cafe ph ni . </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vy u l mn bnh ngt m bn  dng qua Cu t bit c vi mn ngon,  mnh gii thiu n mi ngi nha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>1. Bnh flan</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng u danh sch l mn bnh ht sc quen thuc vi gii tr Vit Nam - bnh flan - c nhiu loi bnh flan khc nhau c sng to n nay. Nhng hng v ca bnh flan truyn thng ha quyn cng c ph en m c vn khng g c th snh bng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":525,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-525\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thnh phn chnh ca bnh flan gm trng, sa v ng trn u vi nhau mang hp chn l bn c mt mn bnh mn bo ngy tuyt vi. Khng ch va ngon m bnh flan cng v cng l giu dinh dng ph hp vi cc bn tr, nhng ngi tp th dc th thao v thm ch l c vi ngi mun gim cn na. V vy khi ung cafe cc bn nht nh hy th chung cng bnh Flan 1 ln xem sao nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>2. Mouse cake</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mn bnh kh kn ngi n nhng chng li l nim am m ca nhng ai thch  ngt. Dng bnh ny c nhiu kem v ch c 1 phn bnh gato mng pha di v th khi n bnh s tan nhanh trong ming vi hng v mm mi, mt lnh v bo ngy ca kem. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":527,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-527\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nguyn liu chnh  lm bnh bao gm lng  trng, kem ti, sa ti v ng. Chng rt hp  dng trong cc ngy k nim nh nhng, nhng v bnh a phn l kem nn lun phi c bo qun  nhit  t 1-3*C. V ngt ca bnh ha quyn cng v ng ca cafe th s nh th no nh? Hy dng cafe ca Cu t v th vi bnh Mouse cake xem no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>3. Cheese cake</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cheese cake mn bnh rt quen thuc vi tt c gii tr Vit Nam v c  hu ht cc hng qun thc ung. Nguyn liu lm ra mn bnh ny thng gm bnh quy, b, ng, trng g v cream Cheese. Theo  cng ty theo c trng m thc ca mi quc gia m c nhiu loi bnh Cheese Cake khc nhau. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":528,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-528\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thnh phn quan trng trong bnh Cheese Cake  Chu u ca h l ph mai. Trang tr bt mt y hp dn, v ngon, bo ngy ca loi bnh ny  thuyt phc khng bit bao nhiu v khch kh tnh. V hy thng thc n trong mt khng gian lng mn cng mt tch c ph.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>4. Bnh Tiramisu</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thm mt mn bnh quen thuc vi gii tr hin nay v cng c lng  phn khc i tng l dn vn phng, mn bnh vi ci tn rt nht nhng xut x th l  . </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":529,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-529\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mn bnh ny c lm t ru Rhum, c ph, ca cao, kem, ph mai v trng. Mn bnh ny rt c phng ty u i khi dng chng vi c ph, hn ht l nhng hng qun ti  nu bn c dp 1 ln gh thm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>5. Cookies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cookies hay mnh cn gi l bnh quy mn bnh d tm d mua v hu nh nh no cng c, n gin v v ngt bo ca n rt bt ming thu ht t tr nh n ngi ln tui. Mn bnh d dng dng chung vi cc loi thc ung mang v cht hoc ng. Nhiu ngi ln tui th thch dng chng vi tr cn chng ta th dng chng vi cafe ph.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":530,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-530\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hy ngh n khung cnh bn ngi bn ca s c sch, nhm nhi ly c ph nng hi bn cnh l mt a bnh ngt nhiu hnh th xinh p, thi thit mt m d chu. Tht s rt th thi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>6. Chocolate tart</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chocolate tart mn bnh n nh trng ming n t phng Ty. Bnh c 2 phn l v bnh cng, hi gin pha ngoi v phn nhn mm bn trong vi nhiu hng v phong ph hp dn. Mn bnh ny khng qu ph bin lm vi ngi Vit mnh. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":531,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-531\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng nu bn mun m qun cafe th hy cho n vo danh sch cc mn trng ming nh, y l mn n yu thch ca ngi phng Ty, bn c th thu ht h vi mn bnh tuyt vi ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>7. Pana Cotta</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhn qua n nh kiu dng ca mn bnh flan ca chng ta Panna Cotta l mn bnh thuc danh sch nhng mn n nh trong qun cafe, cc qun bnh ngt. Bnh c trng bi s mm mn, tan nh trong ming cng hng v nh nhng thanh mt nh thch. Bnh Panna Cotta thu ht thc khch bng v ngt bo ngy ca kem, sa v s ti mt ca cc loi tri cy</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":532,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-532\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>y l danh sch nhng mn  ngt thm ngon khi bn dng chung vi cafe, nu bn mun m mt qun cafe th ng qun cho chng vo danh sch mn trng ming ca qun nh. Quan trng nht l hy dng cafe c sn nguyn cht t Cu t mang n hng v tuyt vi cho thc khch ca bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'im mt 7 mn bnh tuyt vi khi n km vi cafe', 'Mt ly c ph nng hi c dng vi mt mn n km  l mt cch thng thc quen thuc, nht l cc bn tr tui thi nay.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '145-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-20 14:20:31', '2021-08-20 07:20:31', '', 145, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=533', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(535, 2, '2021-08-20 14:21:26', '2021-08-20 07:21:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt ly c ph nng hi c dng vi mt mn n km  l mt cch thng thc quen thuc, nht l cc bn tr tui thi nay. Nhng qun cafe ph tr nn thn thuc hn vi mi tng lp, h n  th gin, hc tp, hay l tm mt khng gian lm vic, ... u c im chung rng rt yu thich  ngt v nhng mn cafe ph ni . </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vy u l mn bnh ngt m bn  dng qua Cu t bit c vi mn ngon,  mnh gii thiu n mi ngi nha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>1. Bnh flan</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng u danh sch l mn bnh ht sc quen thuc vi gii tr Vit Nam - bnh flan - c nhiu loi bnh flan khc nhau c sng to n nay. Nhng hng v ca bnh flan truyn thng ha quyn cng c ph en m c vn khng g c th snh bng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":525,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-525\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thnh phn chnh ca bnh flan gm trng, sa v ng trn u vi nhau mang hp chn l bn c mt mn bnh mn bo ngy tuyt vi. Khng ch va ngon m bnh flan cng v cng l giu dinh dng ph hp vi cc bn tr, nhng ngi tp th dc th thao v thm ch l c vi ngi mun gim cn na. V vy khi ung cafe cc bn nht nh hy th chung cng bnh Flan 1 ln xem sao nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>2. Mouse cake</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mn bnh kh kn ngi n nhng chng li l nim am m ca nhng ai thch  ngt. Dng bnh ny c nhiu kem v ch c 1 phn bnh gato mng pha di v th khi n bnh s tan nhanh trong ming vi hng v mm mi, mt lnh v bo ngy ca kem. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":527,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-527\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nguyn liu chnh  lm bnh bao gm lng  trng, kem ti, sa ti v ng. Chng rt hp  dng trong cc ngy k nim nh nhng, nhng v bnh a phn l kem nn lun phi c bo qun  nhit  t 1-3*C. V ngt ca bnh ha quyn cng v ng ca cafe th s nh th no nh? Hy dng cafe ca Cu t v th vi bnh Mouse cake xem no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>3. Cheese cake</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cheese cake mn bnh rt quen thuc vi tt c gii tr Vit Nam v c  hu ht cc hng qun thc ung. Nguyn liu lm ra mn bnh ny thng gm bnh quy, b, ng, trng g v cream Cheese. Theo  cng ty theo c trng m thc ca mi quc gia m c nhiu loi bnh Cheese Cake khc nhau. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":528,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/diem-mat-7-mon-banh-tuyetvs-an-kem-vs-cafe-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-528\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thnh phn quan trng trong bnh Cheese Cake  Chu u ca h l ph mai. Trang tr bt mt y hp dn, v ngon, bo ngy ca loi bnh ny  thuyt phc khng bit bao nhiu v khch kh tnh. V hy thng thc n trong mt khng gian lng mn cng mt tch c ph.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>4. Bnh Tiramisu</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thm mt mn bnh quen thuc vi gii tr hin nay v cng c lng  phn khc i tng l dn vn phng, mn bnh vi ci tn rt nht nhng xut x th l  . </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":529,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image s