 liu, chng ta cng Cu t tin ti phng php pha c ph sa ng v no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 1: Cho cafe vo phin v nn</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cho vo 2  3 tha cafe bt vo phin, c th gia gim lng bt ph thuc vo  m  c ph m bn mun dng. Ray nh cafe  chng trn u b mt d dng trong vic nn cafe hn. Lu   trnh nc khng thm ht c cafe bn khng nn nn qu cht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 2: Cho sa vo ly</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cho sa c vo ly vi dung tch tng ng vi cafe. D nhin bn c th gia gim ph hp vi khu phn ca mnh, nu mun bo th thm sa, ngt th thm ng hoc thch ng th gim lng sa li.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 3: Thm nc si v  cafe</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>u tin bn phi ri nh nc si cho cafe n ra trong khong 20-30s, sau   chm nc si vo v thao tc phi u tay v khi cafe nh tng git m c thm ngon vi lng nc ph hp. y np v nn cafe, nu c cht th hy kha chng, lu  mc  nn cafe va phi  cafe c p xung v thm u vi nc si. Khng nn  c ph chy qu nhanh s khng ly c ht c tinh cht ca cafe v lm mt hng v, lm gim cht lng khi dng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 4: Thm  v gia gim khu v</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cui cng sau khong thi gian ch i chng ta chun b mt phn  xay nhuyn, i vi vo ngi th thch dng  vin. Ta ha tan phn sa v cafe c lc vi nhau, c mt mo nh l bn c th thm 1 it mui tinh vo cafe  hm bt v chua trong cafe ung s c cm gic thanh hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>n gin vi 4 bc chng ta  c c ly cafe sa yu thch m v ca mnh. Mt mn thc ung n gin d lm m khng tn nhiu thi gian ng khng no. Nu bn bng khung v vic chn la cafe hy n vi Cu t  tri nghim ca ph c sn cht lng cao, cafe Cu t s khng lm bn tht vng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'LM TH NO  PHA MT 