(544, 2, '2021-08-20 19:16:49', '2021-08-20 12:16:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cafe en m v nguyn cht th dnh cho phi mnh, cafe sa ha quyn ngt ngo li thch hp cho nhng qu c v gii tr hin nay.  c mt ly cafe cht lng bn u phi tun th nhiu quy tc nht nh.  y Cu t s ch cho bn cch lm mt ly c ph sa thm ngon ngt ngy nha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":542,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lam-the-nao-de-co-mot-ly-ca-phe-sua-dung-vi-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-542\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>S ha quyn gia sa v hng v c trng ca cafe mang n cho bn mt hng v tuyt vi.  pha c ph ngon trc ht nguyn liu phi nguyn cht khng tm thm ph gia, phi m bo l nguyn liu sch hon ton. C th:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Nu l nguyn liu c ph ht cn chn lc k lng, khng chn loi b m mc, chn loi ht y n vi mu sc ty vo s thch ca ngi ung.</li><li>Nu mua cafe bt rang xay th yu cu khng qu mn cng khng qu th bi  mn v  th ca cafe nh hng ln n cch pha c ph ngon.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>4 Bc pha mt ly c ph sa</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vic ung cafe  l mt nt vn ha ring trong li sng ca ngi Vit Nam.  pha mt ly c ph truyn thng l vic ht sc n gin vi bt k ai. Tuy nhin  c c hng v thm lng, v m , mu sc p th cn phi c phng php v k nng nht nh m khng phi ai cng t c.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> c mt ly c ph ngon i hi khu chun b phi tht cn thn v k lng t cafe bt  xay, phin cafe, sa c c ng. Phin cafe phi tt, c th tch ph hp  m bo  m v ca cafe. c bit, ngi ta dng phin inox tt hn phin nhm v v chng d dng v sinh hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi hon thnh cc bc chn lc v chun b nguyn liu, chng ta cng Cu t tin ti phng php pha c ph sa ng v no.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 1: Cho cafe vo phin v nn</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cho vo 2  3 tha cafe bt vo phin, c th gia gim lng bt ph thuc vo  m  c ph m bn mun dng. Ray nh cafe  chng trn u b mt d dng trong vic nn cafe hn. Lu   trnh nc khng thm ht c cafe bn khng nn nn qu cht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 2: Cho sa vo ly</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cho sa c vo ly vi dung tch tng ng vi cafe. D nhin bn c th gia gim ph hp vi khu phn ca mnh, nu mun bo th thm sa, ngt th thm ng hoc thch ng th gim lng sa li.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":543,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lam-the-nao-de-co-mot-ly-ca-phe-sua-dung-vi-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-543\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 3: Thm nc si v  cafe</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>u tin bn phi ri nh nc si cho cafe n ra trong khong 20-30s, sau   chm nc si vo v thao tc phi u tay v khi cafe nh tng git m c thm ngon vi lng nc ph hp. y np v nn cafe, nu c cht th hy kha chng, lu  mc  nn cafe va phi  cafe c p xung v thm u vi nc si. Khng nn  c ph chy qu nhanh s khng ly c ht c tinh cht ca cafe v lm mt hng v, lm gim cht lng khi dng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Bc 4: Thm  v gia gim khu v</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cui cng sau khong thi gian ch i chng ta chun b mt phn  xay nhuyn, i vi vo ngi th thch dng  vin. Ta ha tan phn sa v cafe c lc vi nhau, c mt mo nh l bn c th thm 1 it mui tinh vo cafe  hm bt v chua trong cafe ung s c cm gic thanh hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>n gin vi 4 bc chng ta  c c ly cafe sa yu thch m v ca mnh. Mt mn thc ung n gin d lm m khng tn nhiu thi gian ng khng no. Nu bn bng khung v vic chn la cafe hy n vi Cu t  tri nghim ca ph c sn cht lng cao, cafe Cu t s khng lm bn tht vng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'LM TH NO  PHA MT LY C PH SA THM NGON NG V', 'Cafe en m v nguyn cht th dnh cho phi mnh, cafe sa ha quyn ngt ngo li thch hp cho nhng qu c v gii tr hin nay. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '290-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-20 19:16:49', '2021-08-20 12:16:49', '', 290, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=544', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
