(580, 2, '2021-08-21 19:14:31', '2021-08-21 12:14:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti Cu t, chng ti trn trng s tin tng ca khch hng khi t mua sn phm. Chnh sch hu mi  Cu t c xy dng da trn cam kt bo v quyn li ngi tiu dng  qu khch c th yn tm mua sm v tri nghim dch v.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cu t m bo sn phm c bn ti Cu t l sn phm mi v 100% chnh hng. Trong trng hp him hoi sn phm qu khch nhn c c khim khuyt, h hng hoc khng nh m t, Cu t cam kt bo v khch hng bng chnh sch i tr v bo hnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>THC HIN I TR VI 03 BC CC K N GIN</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":579,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://caudatweb.vk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/aaa1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-579\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Thi gian p dng i tr: 24 gii (K t khi Cu t giao hng thnh cng).</li><li>Sn phm li: i mi, tr khng thu ph.</li><li>Sn phm khng li, sn phm li do ngi s dng: Khng p dng i tr.</li><li> m bo quyn li khch hng v Cu t c c s lm vic vi cc b phn lin quan, tt c yu cu i/ tr/ bo hnh qu khch cn cung cp hnh nh/clip sn phm li. Cu t xin php t chi khi cha nhn  thng tin hnh nh t qu khch. Bn cnh , qu khch cn quay video clip ng gi sn phm  lm bng chng i chiu/ khiu ni lin quan n i tr v sau (nu cn).</li><li>Bn cnh chnh sch chung v thi gian v iu kin i tr, quy nh i/tr/bo hnh cc sn phm thuc nhm Qa tng km, Sn phm/Dch v mua km, Mua km gim thm c thm mt s iu kin nh sau:</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>QU TNG KM</strong></td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>SN PHM MUA KM/ MUA KM GIM THM</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Sn phm li (do nh cung cp)</strong></td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">i (sn phm chnh b li) hoc Tr nguyn b</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">i sn phm li hoc Tr nguyn b</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Sn phm khng li</strong></td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Tr nguyn b</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Tr nguyn b</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Lu :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Khng p dng i/tr/bo hnh vi sn phm qu tng.</li><li>Ch h tr tr hng nu qu tng/sn phm mua km/sn phm mua theo gi cn nguyn mi v c gi li y .</li><li>Cc trng hp bo hnh s theo chnh sch bo hnh ca nh bn/nh sn xut.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngy hiu lc 19/03/2010, cp nht ln cui 05/05/2020.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Chnh sch i tr', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-21 19:14:31', '2021-08-21 12:14:31', '', 84, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=580', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(582, 2, '2021-08-21 19:37:10', '2021-08-21 12:37:10', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Khu vc p dng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>p dng cho tt c a ch giao hng trong lnh th Vit Nam.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Thi gian giao hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thi gian vn chuyn ph thuc vo kho x l v a ch nhn hng. Qu khch vui lng tham kho thi gian giao hng d kin ti trang sn phm bng cch vo thng tin sn phm, in thng tin vo khu vc giao hng: tnh/thnh, qun/huyn, phng/x.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi hon tt, h thng s thng bo n qu khch thi gian giao hng d kin cho sn phm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngoi ra, qu khch c th kim tra thi gian nhn hng v cc ph vn chuyn ti bc 3 \"Thanh ton&amp; t mua\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*<strong>Lu </strong>: thi gian giao hng trn ch th hin d kin, thc t c th dao ng sm hoc mun hn ty theo sn phm qu khch t mua. Qu khch c th s dng tnh nng \"Tra cu n hng\"  theo di qu trnh x l n hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Ngy hiu lc chnh sch 19/03/2010.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Chnh sch giao hng', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '79-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-21 19:37:10', '2021-08-21 12:37:10', '', 79, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=582', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(584, 2, '2021-08-21 19:41:58', '2021-08-21 12:41:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch c th t hng trc tuyn  website Cu t thng qua cc bc t hng c bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vui lng tham kho thng tin chi tit v tng bc t hng nh sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>1. ng nhp ti khon ti Cu t:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch vui lng ng nhp bng ti khon  c  Cu t hoc ng nhp thng qua Facebook/ Zalo/ Google. Trong trng hp cha ng k ti khon , qu khch c th chn dng To ti khon  ng k ti khon ti Cu t.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi  hon tt, qu khch c th bm vo ch To ti khon  hon tt qu trnh ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>2. Tm kim sn phm:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch c th tm sn phm theo 3 cch:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>G tn sn phm vo thanh tm kim.<br>Tm theo danh mc.<br>Tm theo cc sn phm mi nht, bn chy hoc danh mc ph bin trn tng ngnh hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>3. Thm sn phm vo gi hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi  tm c sn phm mong mun, qu khch vui lng bm vo hnh hoc tn sn phm  vo c trang thng tin chi tit ca sn phm, sau :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kim tra thng tin sn phm: gi, thng tin khuyn mi.<br>Chn s lng mong mun.<br>Thm sn phm vo gi hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi  thao tc b sn phm u tin vo n hng, qu khch vui lng thc hin cc bc sau  thm cc sn phm khc vo gi hng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chn vo logo Cu t  tr v trang ch hoc g tm kim sn phm trn thanh cng c.<br>Thm sn phm vo gi hng bng cch chn s lng v Chn mua.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Qu trnh ny c th lp li cho n khi qu khch hon tt vic b tt c cc sn phm cn t mua vo gi hng</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>4. Kim tra gi hng v t hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qu khch c th t cc sn phm khc nhau trong 1 gi hng thnh 1 n hng, cc sn phm trong gi hng s c ng thnh 1 kin hng (nu sn phm thuc cng 1 nh cung cp/kho x l) v giao n a ch qu khch  ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi qu khch  c  sn phm cn t trong gi hng, vui lng m gim gi (nu c) v tip tc cc bc sau  t hng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chn sn phm qu khch mun mua v iu chnh s lng ph hp.<br>Bm Mua hng  bt u t hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>5. iu chnh a ch giao hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>6. Chn phng thc thanh ton, s dng Cu t Xu v t Mua:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cu t h tr giao hng v thanh ton tn ni cho cc n hng c tng tr gi t 20.000.000 tr xung trn ton quc. Qu khch vui lng tham kho thm ti: Cc Phng Thc Thanh Ton</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi hon tt qu trnh chn phng thc thanh ton, vui lng kim tra li cc thng tin sau: xut ha n VAT (nu c), a ch nhn hng, gi khuyn mi, tng tin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu cc thng tin trn  chnh xc, qu khch vui lng bm t Mua, h thng s bt u tin hnh to n hng da trn cc thng tin qu khch  ng k.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>7. Kim tra v xc nhn n hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi hon tt c bc t mua, h thng s gi n qu khch mt m s n hng v thng bo thi gian giao hng d kin, qu khch c th kim tra li n hng bng cch bm vo dng n hng ca ti hoc email xc nhn n hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>8. Theo di tnh trng n hng:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sau khi t hng thnh cng, qu khch c th theo di tin trnh x l v vn chuyn ca n hng bng cch ng nhp vo ng link:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>L<strong>u :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cu t khuyn khch qu khch t thao tc t hng  c th tham gia u i v theo di tnh trng n hng. Trng hp qu khch yu cu Cu t h tr t hng thay Cu t rt tic cha p dng Cu t Xu, bookcare, coupon cho n hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Hng dn mua hng', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-21 19:41:58', '2021-08-21 12:41:58', '', 78, 'http://caudatweb.vk/?p=584', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
