(8465, 'If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.', 'Nu bn sa hoc cng b bi vit, mt bn cookie b sung s c lu trong trnh duyt. Cookie ny khng cha thng tin c nhn v ch n gin bao gm ID ca bi vit bn  sa. N t ng ht hn sau 1 ngy.', 'default', 2),
